 💬</p><p>Topic 📑 AI-Driven Sales &amp\; Marketing: <b>Lessons learned from
  Appical</b></p><p><strong>Join us for a first-hand look at how Appical is 
 using AI to transform sales and marketing.</strong><br>Managing Director<a 
 href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/wietskevanhees/" target="_blank"> <strong
 >Wietske van Hees</strong></a> will share how her team experiments with AI 
 to drive smarter prospecting\, personalized outreach\, and automated proces
 ses that deliver measurable results.  </p><p><a href="https://www.appical.c
 om/" target="_blank">Appical </a>has been experimenting with AI not just to
  improve efficiency but to drive measurable impact across sales and marketi
 ng. At their flagship event\, Onboard Amsterdam\, the team combined multipl
 e AI tools: Clay\, HeyReach\, ChatGPT - to experiment with smart prospectin
 g\, personalized outreach\, and automated marketing processes. The results 
 showed how AI can maximize the funnel and create meaningful engagement\, ev
 en when scaling events was previously under scrutiny.</p><p>In this session
 \, Wietske will share:</p><ul><li><p>An introduction to Appical and her rol
 e as MD</p></li><li><p>How sales and marketing teams are structured and ena
 bled with AI</p></li><li><p>Key tools (Clay\, Apollo\, HeyReach) and use ca
 ses delivering the biggest wins</p></li><li><p>Lessons learned from integra
 ting AI into daily work</p></li></ul><p></p><p><br></p>\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:
